                                                                                                                                Input and selection

                                                                                                                                Select [Deprecated]

                                                                                                                                Deprecated

                                                                                                                                A select is a type of dropdown menu that allows the user to choose from a list of predefined options. It is typically represented on the page as a dropdown menu when the user clicks on it.

                                                                                                                                Usage
                                                                                                                                Status & changelog
                                                                                                                                Specs
                                                                                                                                Common alternative names
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Select box, select input, dropdown, dropdown list


                                                                                                                                ﻿Questions, comments, feedback?

                                                                                                                                Leave a comment in Figma or reach out to us on Slack.

                                                                                                                                #base-design-support


                                                                                                                                Anatomy

                                                                                                                                Select components have the same anatomy as a Text field, with the exception of the added select chevron indicator.

                                                                                                                                States

                                                                                                                                Overview / States

                                                                                                                                Sizes

                                                                                                                                Selects are available in 3 sizes.

                                                                                                                                Large
                                                                                                                                Medium
                                                                                                                                Small

                                                                                                                                Behavior

                                                                                                                                General

                                                                                                                                Empty vs preselected
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Selects may be empty or preselected when a user arrives on the screen.

                                                                                                                                Hint or selected option
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                The select box has different behavior depending on whether you are interacting with it the first time, vs if you have already selected something.

                                                                                                                                Standalone vs Combined with Input
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Selects may be standalone or may be combined with a standard Input. Combined versions are detailed to the right in the Select Input section.

                                                                                                                                Mobile

                                                                                                                                Option 1
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                iOS picker. Intended for shorter lists of items.

                                                                                                                                Option 2
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                A full modal picker. Intended for longer lists of items.

                                                                                                                                Desktop

                                                                                                                                Desktop
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Desktop select inputs offer a simple dropdown.
